                                    <h2> Mehun d.o.o. </h2>
                                    <p> Health service company with a dental technique laboratory Mehun d.o.o. is one of the first among such companies in Croatia. <strong>We started out in 1992 and our wish was to apply our acquirement and practical knowledge in a best possible way.</strong> Since that time we can be proud of many of our high quality works. The best confirmation for that comes from our associates and it can be seen in thousands smiles on our satisfied patients' faces. </p>
