                    <!-- Stupac niže lijevo-->
                    <div class="column_left">
                        <p>MEHUN d.o.o. has 14 employees and as such it is considered as a small firm. For 22 years, our employees have been going through permanent training, development and education in different areas of dental technique. Therefore, they are capable to solve the biggest challenges, whether in processes and approaches to making dental prosthetic replacements or in materials that are being used. We follow the latest achievements and with our equipement and competence we are at the highest level of dental technique, in areas which we cover with our work. Owner of our firm, Mr <strong>Darko Mehun</strong>, and our laboratory manager, Ms <strong>Sanja Ciberlin</strong>, cooperate with some of the most important experts, their approach to all recent scientific methods is open and evident and their experience is rich and wide. All of that enables our co-workers and associates an individual approach in resolving different cases and also, they can always get a good and professional advice. </p>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Stupac niže desno-->
                    <div class="column_right">
                        <p>In the past few years, the firm is particularly interested in non-metal solutions and materials which are the least uncomfortable for the patients, but also for dentists. <br>
                            <br>
                            Our laboratory employees are capable to carry out and accomplish every required job – <strong>from whitening foils through anti-snoring device to the most complicated implant works with all materials: base metals, plates, zircon-oxides, titanium. Laboratory's specialty is making facial epithesis, nose and ear prosthetic, etc.</strong> Along with basic services, interests of our firm are also extended to education. <br>
                        </p>
                    </div>
