                            <h4 class="box_header"> About our director and about our laboratory manager </h4>
                            <li class="item_content clearfix"> <a class="features_image" title="Darko Mehun"> <img src="{{ asset('images/darko_mehun.jpg') }}" alt="Darko Mehun" /> </a>
                                <div class="bio"> <strong>Darko Mehun, director</strong><br>
                                    <br>
                                    He has been practicing dental technique since 1981. 11 years later he became an owner of a dental laboratory. During 1990's he was intensively involved in education in different areas of dental technique. In 1998 he signed his first contract with Degussa dental company and with that he became a demonstrator of company's alloy products, all sorts of ceramics and snythetic resins. In 2003, he starts to cooperate with DeguDent company, and since 2013 he has been OPL for a complete Dentsply production program, with an emphasis on CAD CAM technology. He has also been a technical advisor for a whole area from Poland to Israel. He is fluent in several languages and, as a lecturer, he has been participating on congresses and workshops in Southeastern Europe. Knowledge and experience that he gained through his work and education he shares with his colleagues and he helps with development and better work quality in his profession. </div>
                            </li>
                            <li class="item_content clearfix"> <a class="features_image" title="Sanja Ciberlin"> <img src="{{ asset('images/sanja_ciberlin.jpg') }}" alt="Sanja Ciberlin" /> </a>
                                <div class="bio"> <strong>Sanja Ciberlin, manager</strong><br>
                                    <br>
                                    She had a short experience as a dental techician at "Perkovčeva" Dental Polyclinic. Since 1994, for some time she was an associate at a dental laboratory and later, since 2005 also at our firm "Mehun d.o.o.". Through first ten years of 2000's she went through intensive education in dental ceramics and gnatology areas and she became a specialist for dental ceramics. In 2007, with her serious approach to work, she became assistant manager. Since 2013 her position has been a manager at our laboratory. Twenty years of experience and devotion to her work enable her to solve the most difficult cases with easiness and fluency.  </div>
